import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'

import App from './App'

import axios from 'axios'

axios
.get('http://localhost:3001/notes')
.then(response => {
  const notes = response.data
  console.log(notes)
})


ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root')).render(
  <App notes={notes} />
)
